Compliance and Verification
The Licensee agrees to configure the Software in accordance with the provided
documentation, including proper setup of the Interactive Brokers Trader
Workstation (TWS) API settings (e.g., enabling socket connections on port 7497
for paper accounts or 7496 for live accounts). The Licensor may require
verification of compliance with the Paper Account restriction, and the Licensee
agrees to provide reasonable evidence of such compliance upon request.

